name: WARUNG NASI MEN MANGKOK
address: Jl. Kertanegara No.62, Ubung Kaja, Kec. Denpasar Utara, Kota Denpasar, Bali 80115, Indonesia
review 1:
This place is very popular place among the locals here, do you know why ? Because it's taste! Yes ! Taste never lie here , so good and delicious local meals , here they served very delicious Balinese rice porridge with Balinese vegetables mixed with pork well known as "lawar" is various spices cooked and mixed to created special dish called lawar , and if you don't like rice porridge ,they have steamed rice as well mixed with various cooked meat
Worth to try if you around north Denpasar , by the way you have to come in the morning around 6 to 9 am to get this delicious breakfast meals
